746
00:48:42,520 --> 00:48:44,280
Charles resents me.

747
00:48:44,920 --> 00:48:48,280
Anne resents me. And is it possible
that you resent me too?

748
00:48:48,360 --> 00:48:50,880
All I want is to play for the team.

749
00:48:51,440 --> 00:48:52,760
You're the Princess of Wales.

750
00:48:52,840 --> 00:48:55,200
- So of course you're part of the team.
- Then show me.

751
00:48:56,840 --> 00:48:59,560
This whole thing,
it starts and stops with you.

752
00:49:00,240 --> 00:49:01,760
You're the captain of the team.

753
00:49:02,280 --> 00:49:05,960
If you show me love,
approval, and acceptance,

754
00:49:06,040 --> 00:49:07,640
everyone else will follow.

755
00:49:08,160 --> 00:49:10,440
I think
we've gone as far as we can for now.

756
00:49:10,520 --> 00:49:13,240
