- Don't dismiss me, please.

757
00:49:13,760 --> 00:49:14,760
Don't push me away.

758
00:49:14,840 --> 00:49:16,720
- What?
- Mama…

759
00:49:34,160 --> 00:49:35,240
That's all I want.

760
00:49:38,800 --> 00:49:40,760
It's all any of us want from you.

761
00:49:42,120 --> 00:49:43,480
Is it too much to ask?

762
00:50:00,000 --> 00:50:01,080
<i>A hug?</i>

763
00:50:01,160 --> 00:50:02,160
Yes.

764
00:50:02,960 --> 00:50:04,000
